channel.name: HL7 Scrub Data
channel.description:
This shows a simple module to scrub data from an HL7 feed.
See http://help.interfaceware.com/v6/hl7-scrub
This useful if you want to share this data with another party but do not wish to violate patient confidentiality.

to_mapper.commit_comment: Put in more comments and 'hydration routine'.
